*
******************************************************************************
*  Model performance : 
*  - Static Electrical Characteristics and Dynamic Electrical Characteristics 
*    are modeled with the typical values from the datasheet.
*  - Temperature effects are modeled
*
*  The following features have been modeled :
*  - Switching Characteristics such as propagation delay, peak currents, output resistance
*  - Undervoltage lockout 
*  - Current consumption
******************************************************************************
* PINS:
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | NAME    | DESCRIPTION 
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | IN+     | Connected to PWM output controller via 47 kohm or 75 kohm resistor 
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | IN-     | Connected to controller ground via 47 kohm or 75 kohm resistor 
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | VSS     | Return path for VDD and thermal dissipation pad 
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | VDD     | Gate drive supply 
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | BST     | Bootstrap diode anode connection point, when used as low-side driver in a half-bridge configuration 
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | OUT_SNK | Low-impedance gate pull-down to VOFF (including active Miller clamp) 
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | OUT_SRC | Low-impedance gate pull-up to VDD 
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | TAMB    | Ambient temperature 
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | TJ      | Junction temperature 
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*
******************************************************************************
